=== Featured list ===
VRChat maintains a curated list of featured [[Special:MyLanguage/Public Avatars|public avatars]], which are optimized for performance and designed to cater to various styles and preferences. Users can browse and try on these avatars at any time by navigating to the [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]] tab within the [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]], selecting the "Avatar" section and scroll down to the "Publics" row.